  <description type="morphology">Plants 15–180 cm. Stems densely tomentose. Leaves: blades oblanceolate or
        oblong-elliptic, 10–30 cm, shallowly to deeply pinnatifid, main spines mostly 5–10 mm,
        abaxial faces loosely tomentose. Heads 1–10. Involucres 4–5 × 5–7 cm, ± densely tomentose.
        Phyllaries: outer and middle bodies scabridulous or minutely spinulose, marginal spinules
        usually 1 mm or shorter. Corollas yellow or crimson to red-purple. 2n = 32,
        34.</description>
